+--------------------------------+                         
|         MQTT Client Manager    |
|--------------------------------|
| - Manages multiple servers     |
| - Coordinates subscriptions    |
| - Handles decoding             |
+---------------+----------------+
                |
                |
+---------------+----------------+
|          Server Manager        |
|--------------------------------|
| - Connects/disconnects to/from |
|   MQTT servers                 |
| - Manages server parameters    |
+---------------+----------------+
                |
                |
+---------------+----------------+
|          Topic Manager         |
|--------------------------------|
| - Adds/removes topics          |
| - Associates topics with       |
|   servers                      |
+---------------+----------------+
                |
                |
+---------------+----------------+
|        Decoder Manager         |
|--------------------------------|
| - Adds/removes decoders        |
| - Decodes messages based on    |
|   topics                       |
+---------------+----------------+
                |
                |
+---------------+----------------+
|        Database Manager        |
|--------------------------------|
| - Manages database operations  |
| - Uses SQLAlchemy              |
+---------------+----------------+
